            <div type="translation">
                <p>Ὁ ἅγιος Δημήτριος. Θεοτόκε βοήθει τῷ σῷ δούλῳ / Ὑπατίῳ σπαθαροκανδιδάτῳ ἀσηκρῆτις καὶ κριτῇ Καππαδοκίας.</p>
                <p xml:lang="en">St. Demetrios. Mother of God, help your servant Hypatios spatharokandidatos, asekretis, and krites of Cappadocia.</p>
                <p xml:lang="de">Hl. Demetrios. Muttergottes, hilf deinem Diener Hypatios spatharokandidatos, asekretis und krites von Kappadokien.</p>
              </div>
            <div type="commentary" subtype="text">
                <p xml:lang="en">The name of the issuer is quite unusual, and in fact Schlumberger read the name on his seal as Akatios.[1]</p>
                  <p xml:lang="de"/>
